<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-card>
        <v-card-title>
            Dashboard
        </v-card-title>
        <v-card-subtitle>
        <v-breadcrumbs :items="items">
            <template v-slot:divider>
                <v-icon>mdi-chevron-right</v-icon>
            </template>
        </v-breadcrumbs>
        </v-card-subtitle>
    </v-card>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data: () => ({
      items: [
        {
          text: 'Dashboard',
          disabled: false,
          href: 'breadcrumbs_dashboard',
        },
        {
          text: 'Link 1',
          disabled: false,
          href: 'breadcrumbs_link_1',
        },
        {
          text: 'Link 2',
          disabled: true,
          href: 'breadcrumbs_link_2',
        },
      ],
    }),
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
